data.description: 3 bedroom, 1 bath ranch on a park like 2.82 acres! If in the country, but close to town is what you are looking for this home is for you! Seller has made many improvements to this home:metal roof, new furnace, new flooring in kitchen & hall, new gutter with leaf guard installed, b-dry system in storm cellar, new back door, replacement windows. This home has a sunroof across the back, big covered porch across the front. 2 car carport and a large shed are included.
